    "description": "Língua follows the adventure of Beto, a boy who lives in the rural northeast of Brazil. When the last of his small farm's animals goes missing, he sets out to explore the brazilian caatinga and bumps into a magical part of his world, meeting folkloric characters and helping them in a very important mission that will take him on a hybrid journey of magic and reality!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702450/extras/e226df33ecb87e86013e9afcc5b8fd11.poster.avif?t=1633197652\" width=600 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702450/extras/e226df33ecb87e86013e9afcc5b8fd11.webm?t=1633197652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702450/extras/e226df33ecb87e86013e9afcc5b8fd11.mp4?t=1633197652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Solve puzzles!</strong><br>   Use the resources Beto finds in his journey to interact with elements of his surroundings and advance to your next destination!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702450/extras/4bd2587f010c51134ff0e5923a7c7f63.poster.avif?t=1633197652\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702450/extras/4bd2587f010c51134ff0e5923a7c7f63.webm?t=1633197652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702450/extras/4bd2587f010c51134ff0e5923a7c7f63.mp4?t=1633197652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Free spirits!</strong><br>   Use your magic slingshot to help animal spirits find their way to the beyond in bullet hell style battles!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702450/extras/6076db0fe2656b61e8abedaa9b042a58.poster.avif?t=1633197652\" width=600 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702450/extras/6076db0fe2656b61e8abedaa9b042a58.webm?t=1633197652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702450/extras/6076db0fe2656b61e8abedaa9b042a58.mp4?t=1633197652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Finish quests!</strong><br>   Help locals solve their problems through trading, exploration and minigames!",
